## 🌾 Agri-Expert: Enterprise MLOps & Credit-Risk Intelligence Ecosystem

image.png


### An End-to-End Decision Support System for Precision Agriculture & Financial Inclusion

#### 🏛️ Executive Summary

This project implements a comprehensive production architecture for the agricultural sector. Its core objective is to industrialize the transformation of raw pedological data into Actionable Intelligence. Beyond technical prediction, this system acts as a Financial Bridge: by providing precise risk assessments and mitigation plans, it enables financial institutions to confidently grant loans to farmers, backing credit decisions with rigorous data science.

The system is distinguished by a Medallion Data Architecture, an S3-compatible distributed storage environment (MinIO), and a Self-Healing model protocol powered by ZenML.

#### 🏗️ Technical Architecture & Data Strategy

##### 1. High-Performance Data Engineering (Medallion Pipeline)

To ensure absolute Data Lineage and consistency, the system follows a three-tier abstraction:

Bronze Layer (Ingestion): Immutable ingestion of raw .csv data into MinIO. This serves as the historical "Source of Truth," allowing for complete pipeline re-runs and auditability.

Silver Layer (Processing): silver_pipeline.py. Implements rigorous data cleaning, schema enforcement, and complex missing-value imputation.

Gold Layer (Feature Store): gold_pipeline.py. Orchestrates business-ready features. Data is migrated via minio_to_postgres.py into a PostgreSQL Data Warehouse, enabling high-performance analytical queries for credit-risk profiling.

##### 2. MLOps Excellence & Model Resilience
ZenML Tracking Orchestration: Integration of ZenML to monitor every model iteration. This "Metadata Store" provides total traceability of hyperparameters, metrics, and artifact versions.

Automated Production Flow: A central orchestrator, run_pipeline.py, ensures atomic execution of the entire workflow from preprocessing to deployment, eliminating human error in the production cycle.

FixModel Protocol (Self-Healing Strategy): The fixmodel.py script implements a failover strategy. If a crash or anomaly is detected in production, it automatically restores the most recent stable configuration validated by ZenML, ensuring critical service continuity.

#### 📂 Services & Intelligent Decision Layer

The ecosystem is designed as a suite of containerized microservices, facilitating independent scalability and maintenance

#### 🚀 Inference Microservice (FastAPI)

Located in /services/inference_api, this service exposes the model via a RESTful interface.

Decoupled Logic: Separates statistical computation (Probability Score) from business logic (Credit-Risk Labels).

Fintech Integration: Provides the "Green Label" standards required for automated credit approval.

🎨 Expert Decision Interface (Streamlit)
A rich UI designed for both field operators and financial auditors:

Persistence & Stability: Intensive use of st.session_state to manage application memory, preventing state-loss during complex user interactions.

Mitigation Intelligence (get_advisory): A business-rule engine that interprets model outputs into technical recommendations (e.g., liming protocols, hydraulic management).

Bimodal Communication: Integration of gTTS for dynamic voice synthesis. The AI narrates diagnostics and action plans, optimizing accessibility for "hands-free" field usage.

#### 🛠️ Infrastructure & Deployment Guide

#### Phase 1: Virtualization & Environment Control

Bash
# Environment isolation
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Unix/macOS
venv\Scripts\activate     # Windows

# Deterministic dependency installation
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
python -m pip install -r requirements.txt
$env:PYTHONUTF8 = 1


#### Phase 2: Dockerized Ecosystem (The Essence)
The entire system is orchestrated via Docker Compose, managing internal networks between MinIO, Postgres, the API, and the UI.

Bash
# Deploy the full infrastructure in detached mode
docker compose up --build -d

#### Phase 3: Production Run

Bash
# Execute the end-to-end production pipeline
python production/run_pipeline.py


Object Storage	/Data Lake Storage (S3 API Compliance) /MinIO
Data Warehouse	/Structured Feature & Prediction Persistence /PostgreSQL
Tracking	Pipeline /Lineage & Metadata Governance	/ ZenML
Inference / Real-time Model Serving & Credit Scoring /FastAPI
User Interface	/Decision Intelligence & Voice Synthesis / Streamlit - gTTS

