his project illustrates a high level of ML Pipeline Maturity. It is not merely an academic exercise but a resilient, modular, and production-ready architecture. By merging Statistical Engineering with modern Software Craftsmanship, it offers a robust solution for precision agriculture and financial empowerment in the primary sector.

